snippet.title: Maplewood Junior High 2 - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Play the game at http://carmelgames.com/maplewood-junior-high-2/
---
Every teacher must have a good cup of coffee before starting the day, and Erikka is no exception, but the coffee machine in the teacher's lounge is broken!
Can you fix it?
